## Current Issues & Recommendations

### 1. 🔒 Missing Input Parsing Middleware
The app has no body parser, meaning any `POST`/`PUT` routes you add later would silently receive `undefined` bodies. Add these early:

```js
app.use(express.json({ limit: '10kb' })); // Limit payload size to prevent DoS
